title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Sep 15 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Sep 15 2022
description:
John Fetterman has repeatedly said he wanted to release a third of the prison population. Clay says, "John Fetterman is the worst candidate that has ever been put forward in the modern era for a competitive statewide race... He's a disgrace. He's a disaster. And it will be indefensible if the people of Pennsylvania select him as their next senator." Tampa Bay Lightning backs down, says they did not leave WFLA for political reasons. Miranda Devine of the New York Post joins Clay and Buck to discuss her latest blockbuster story: Facebook spied on private messages of users who questioned the 2020 election. Rand Paul eviscerates Fauci again at hearing.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
